## Disclaimer

This project is for **educational and research purposes only**. It does not constitute investment advice or a recommendation to buy or sell any securities. Past performance does not guarantee future results. The strategy exhibits high beta exposure and significant transaction costs that would materially impact real-world implementation.

**Key Risks:**
- High market beta (2.43) means strategy amplifies market movements
- 94% turnover creates substantial transaction costs
- Survivorship bias in data (uses current S&P 500 constituents)
- Momentum factor showed negative spread in test period

Always conduct your own research and consult with a qualified financial advisor before making investment decisions.

